2) If everything looks good and looks like a trend maybe trying to add at the beginning is ideal, so after taking out 2 contracts, maybe start adding 2 in again at the start and afterwards only 1 or something like that because now it was 2 on, 1 off, then 1 on again (so now 2) and repeating that pattern the whole time.
